ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 269, Yukon
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER No. 269 in order to (1) declare the natural disaster to be of concern to the federal government; and (2) authorize the provision of financial assistance to Yukon with respect to the landslide that occurred on April 8, 2023.
